query:
SELECT 
  s.id,
  s.token,
  s.gestanteId,
  s.expiraEm,
  s.createdAt,
  g.nome,
  g.email,
  CASE 
    WHEN s.expiraEm > NOW() THEN 'VÁLIDA'
    ELSE 'EXPIRADA'
  END as status_sessao
FROM sessoesGestante s
JOIN gestantes g ON s.gestanteId = g.id
WHERE g.email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
ORDER BY s.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
